data.description: A lovely spacious 4 bedroom home just minutes from Batesville. Huge main bedroom with garden tub in main bath. Kitchen is large with a lot of cabinets and fantastic pantry, breakfast area, plus a formal dining room. Enjoy the country style living in a beautiful neighborhood. The home is move in ready and the yard is spacious with fenced backyard.
